title: Waka Flocka - The Turn Up Godz Tour
description:
Bitrate: 128-160 Kbps

Before they set off on tour together, Waka Flocka and DJ Whoo Kid decide to come through and treat fans to a new project called The Turn Up Godz Tour.

Laced with 13 tracks, the project features guest appearances from Howard Stern, Gucci Mane, Future, Offset (of Migos), Ca$h Out, Machine Gun Kelly, and Tony Yayo, among many others. 

Look out for a higher quality upload from yours truly if it becomes available.

Source: hotnewhiphop.com 

Good vibes and love to all, happy jamming
